<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV53">
<l>vārā yiṉamulai yāḷivaḷ vāṉōr talaimakaṉāñ</l>
<l>cīrā yiṉateyva naṉṉō yituteyvat taṇṇantuḻāyt</l>
<l>tārā yiṉuntaḻai yāyiṉun taṇkompa tāyiṉuṅkīḻ</l>
<l>vērā yiṉuniṉṟa maṇṇāyi ṉuṅkoṇṭu vīcumiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In her who has breasts that are high this is the good pain, [due] to the god</l>
<l>who is excellence, who is the leader of the celestials. Be it a garland</l>
<l>of divine cool Tulsi, be it [its] foliage, be it a cool twig, be it from under</l> 
<l>the roots, be it the earth where [it] stands, take [it] and fling [it at her].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
